### Create Patient
POST http://localhost:5000/api/patients
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patientId": "P001",
  "name": "James Osei",
  "age": 45,
  "condition": "Post-Op Cardiac",
  "ward": "ICU"
}

### Get All Patients
GET http://localhost:5000/api/patients

### Post Fake Vitals (simulates ESP32)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/vitals/P001
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "heartRate": 115,
  "spo2": 91,
  "temperature": 38.8,
  "respRate": 26,
  "systolic": 95,
  "diastolic": 62
}

### Ask AI Doctor
POST http://localhost:5000/api/ai/P001
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "What is wrong with this patient and what should I do?",
  "askedBy": "nurse"
}

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:5000/health